rows.label: qst650106_msg0001
rows.name:
Looks like the information you got out
of that goon was right on the money.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0002
rows.name: What's our move, chaps?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, we've established that we're the
targets. I'd say this is our problem to
deal with.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0004
rows.name: We shouldn't just rush in...

rows.label: qst650106_msg0005
rows.name:
Nonsense. They are enemies.
Our directive is clear.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0006
rows.name: T-elos Re:?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0007
rows.name: That girl!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0008
rows.name: Looks like you're not finished yet.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0009
rows.name:
Did you really think you were going
to be able to take down the Holy Grail
and her companions?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0010
rows.name: Who are you?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0011
rows.name: We've been preempted!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0012
rows.name:
Not so. This just saves us the effort
of chasing the Holy Grail down.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0013
rows.name:
These fools are nothing but moths
eager for the flame.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0014
rows.name:
Soon enough, the other survivors of
Acedia will be arriving here.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0015
rows.name:
If we can hold out until then, the hour
of our vengeance will soon be at hand!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0016
rows.name:
Heh.
Risible.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0017
rows.name:
I suppose all you worms
think the same.

rows.label: qst650106_msg0018
rows.name:
You think your threats are anything
more than the chitter of vermin?

rows.label: qst650106_msg0019
rows.name:
You're only one Blade!
Don't underestimate our power!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0020
rows.name: Get her!

rows.label: qst650106_msg0021
rows.name:
Don't get in my way.
I plan on enjoying this.
